Content:
I mentioned it a while back but seems relevant to this talk, we should see how well our RPCs and software works with IoT devices. I know there has been some full node advances on small devices, and nSPV is advancing. We could push some of these types of docs to Zerynth, Particle, and some others that provide IoT hardware/software/middleware.

It's hard for us to imagine every use case but might be better for IoT devs to see our docs in their channels
